////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
// EquiRec_SpirographSpectrum  by mojovideotech
//
// Spherical / Equirectangular version of 
// interactiveshaderformat.com/sketches/1394
//
// based on :
// www.shadertoy.com/\view/\lddGD4
//
